crafting characters, (necessarily) disappoint role murder victim, edward ratchett. imbuing unsavory character dopiest gangster mannerisms, mr. depp may remind matt leblanc’s “friends” character, joey tribbiani. it’s joey, lovable bad actor, trying make first big break movies.
