general counsel convened dinner celebrate.in phone conversation, firm’s general counsel told menu dinner featured photograph me, placed inside red circle slash though it. general counsel told scoured web right picture. menu garnered lots laughs attendees, added.i never find celebration cost firm’s shareholders.incidents like that, however, relatively rare. far outweighed appreciation readers expressed.“you must continue work skewering people customs capitalist society abuse process,” reader jackson, miss., wrote 2001. others expressed thanks “a good consistent questioner,” writing “financially illiterate,” pushing make rules investing fair firm.and loved receiving christmas card reader maryland couple years ago simply said: “thank telling truth!”believe me, privilege.
