alternatives opioids pain relief combination tylenol advil worked well opioids relief pain emergency room, randomized trial found.researchers studied 416 men women arrived e.r. moderate severe pain arms legs sprains, strains, fractures injuries. randomly assigned oral dose acetaminophen (tylenol) either ibuprofen (advil) opioids oxycodone, hydrocodone codeine. two hours later, questioned using 11-point pain scale.the average score 8.7 taking medicine. score decreased 4.3 points ibuprofen tylenol, 4.4 oxycodone tylenol, 3.5 hydrocodone tylenol, 3.9 codeine tylenol. words, significant difference, either statistically clinically, among four regimens. study jama.the lead author, dr. andrew k. chang, professor emergency medicine albany medical college, said single patient might find opioids effective, average, even severe pain fractures, non-opioids worked well.“some docs reflexively give opioid anyone fracture,” dr. chang said. “but give non-opioid show patient works, help ongoing opioid problem.”
ketones rev workouts? ketone supplements supposed mimic effects high-fat, low-carb diet become popular recently among athletes looking performance boost.but new study suggests supplements may work advertised could kinds gastrointestinal side effects make starting, let alone completing, event almost impossible.anyone spends time around serious endurance athletes advisers probably heard chatter enthusiasm high-fat, low-carb diets. diets supposed enable body become better able use fat fuel.carbohydrates are, course, body’s preferred source quick fuel muscles activity. bodies store relatively small amounts may almost exhaust stores prolonged intense exertion, forcing us slow stop.but us plentiful stores fat. became able efficiently use source exercise fuel, could continue longer intensively (and also, desired, rid excess body fat).inspired possibility, athletes nutritionists tout diets contain almost carbohydrates large amounts fat. time, diets lower body’s stores carbohydrates require burn fat almost exclusively.such diets also result abundance ketones, substances produced liver muscles brain use fuel.the problem takes weeks or, commonly, months body adjust low-carbohydrate diet. interim, athletic performance suffers people feel sluggish unwell, sometimes developing condition known “ketone flu” resembles food poisoning.so athletes advisers begun wonder whether taking ketone supplements might allow athletes gain benefits high-fat diet without long, difficult transition time. various types supplements, form powders drinks, chemically identical ketones made body. also widely available many stores and, now, legal international doping regulations.last year, much-discussed study conducted researchers oxford university found proprietary type ketone supplement improved cycling performance group trained riders.but study looked relatively moderate exercise, kind intense exertion required competition.so new study, published last month frontiers physiology, scientists australian institute sport institutions decided create real-world test ketone supplementation.conveniently, ready-made group volunteers 11 members men’s professional, world-class bicycling team begin preseason training australia. team’s members, ridden tour de france international events, keenly interested possible benefits ketone supplements, according louise burke, head sports nutrition australian institute sport study’s senior author.the experiment scientists concocted simple. hour training session, gave rider drink contained either ketones placebo. drinks looked tasted much same. riders second dose drink immediately starting. (the drink used is, far, available research purposes sale public.)then men rode stationary bicycles programmed recreate screen 31-kilometer (about 19 miles) course 2017 road-cycling world championship. riders virtually raced highest pace power output could maintain.each rider rode drinking placebo and, another day, swallowing ketones.the results unanimous. every rider performed worse drinking ketone supplement. times 2 percent slower power output almost 4 percent less, declines that, actual competition, would drop contention medals.every rider also reported degree gastrointestinal upset drinking ketone supplement. one experienced “prolonged vomiting dizziness,” scientists reported, could start time trial. others symptoms ranging dry retching relatively mild nausea.not surprisingly, riders guessed trial ketones, based stomachs’ reactions. told scientists thought riding faster trial, pedaling felt difficult. told performance fact declined, almost announced longer interested using ketones performance enhancement.this study short-term, however. possible riders stomachs might adjust supplement time perhaps gain benefits, dr. burke says. study also show whether stomach upset alone clobbered riders’ performance physiological processes involved. riders’ brains could interpreted sudden presence ketones indicating metabolic problem, dr. burke says, responded sending messages muscles urging slow down.the upshot far research needs conducted experts make recommendations ketone supplementation athletes, dr. burke says. “everyone wants simple answers,” says, body’s mechanisms complex allow that, especially sports.in meantime, one practical caveat bear mind currently available supplements, says. almost “taste nasty.”
pesticides tied problems assisted pregnancies eating fruits vegetables high pesticides may lower chance successful birth assisted reproductive technology, according new report.researchers studied 325 women undergoing fertility treatment boston. collected data medical lifestyle factors women fill food frequency questionnaires. using data united states department agriculture, samples produce pesticide residue, calculated amount residue women ate. list fruits vegetables “pesticide residue score” appears study, published jama internal medicine.the 325 women 228 live births. women highest one-quarter high-pesticide residue produce consumption 18 percent lower probability pregnancy 26 percent lower probability live birth lowest one-quarter.the senior author, dr. jorge e. chavarro, associate professor nutrition harvard t.h. chan school public health, noted one study, would replicated firm conclusions drawn.still, said, “if really want eat peaches spinach” — two contaminated foods list — “it makes sense switch organic version. literature clear whether switching health consequences. first study knowledge suggest does.”
women likely men die first year heart attack compared men, women significantly higher risk death first year heart attack, new study found.the generally higher risk death women heart attacks well known, differences largely explained women’s older age attack occurs, higher rates diseases, types treatment typically receive.this new analysis, published plos one, controlled variables others. researchers studied 802 men 802 women matched age, hypertension, diabetes, smoking status, various measures heart function types treatment medications received.in first year five-year follow-up, women 60 percent likely die male counterparts. beyond first year, men’s women’s death rates differ.the reasons unclear, authors suggest higher levels psychological stress depression women may play role. data assess factors.“we follow female patients carefully,” said senior author, dr. georg schmidt, professor cardiology technical university munich germany. “as doctors, ask patients concerns, look opportunities support beyond drugs standard treatments.”
delhi, blanketed toxic haze, ‘has become gas chamber’ new delhi — toxic haze blanketing new delhi severe tuesday politicians announced plans close schools, flights delayed chief minister delhi state said city “become gas chamber.”for arvind kumar, chest surgeon three decades, situation adding growing health crisis region. “i don’t see pink lungs even among healthy nonsmoking young people,” said telephone interview tuesday. “the air quality become bad even nonsmoker still suffering.”the thick, acrid fog new delhi, settles around time every year, covering capital vehicle emissions smoke burning crops neighboring states fireworks diwali, hindu festival lights. recent years, problem appears worsened.on tuesday, levels dangerous air particles, called pm 2.5, reached 700 micrograms per cubic meter parts city, according data united states embassy. experts say prolonged exposure high concentrations pm 2.5 equivalent smoking two packs cigarettes day.officials struggled control pollution national capital region, includes delhi home 45 million people. ban sale firecrackers diwali october appeared keep problem check, illegal burning crops, contributes significantly pollution time year, started.the situation prompted state’s chief minister, arvind kejriwal, say twitter: “delhi become gas chamber. every year happens part year. find soln crop burning adjoining states.”imran hussain, environment minister delhi, said twitter august written officials states haryana, punjab, rajasthan uttar pradesh requesting reduction agricultural fires, action taken, government spokesman said twitter tuesday.the fires, combined car exhaust, smokestack emissions burning garbage, contribute pollution levels often hover “severe” category, highest level designated central pollution control board.an article last month medical journal lancet found pollution responsible 2.5 million deaths india 2015, country.manish sisodia, deputy chief minister delhi, said tuesday “all options” reducing pollution consider