michelangelo divine star must-see show season “michelangelo: divine draftsman designer” metropolitan museum art monument monument. 200 works, core group 133 drawings beyond-famous artist — largest number ever assembled — loan 50 front-rank collections, it’s curatorial coup. important, it’s art historical tour de force: panoptic view titanic career recorded fragile media — paper, chalk, ink.it’s show demands: requires fully present. snapping smartphones won’t do. drawing graphic experience; it’s textural one, pressure crayon pen page; subliminal fade focus lines; weave shadow-creating swells surfaces. barely seeable, never mind photographable, effects are, one way another, truest evidence artist’s hand.and final drumroll: fame michelangelo buonarroti may last long, met-built monument him, opens monday, nov. 13, not. it’s one-stop event non-extendable three-month run, maximum exposure light, even dusk-level, drawings safely stand. show’s done, likelihood another scale within lifetime anyone reading words slim.giving full account anyone’s art means giving sense came from, get here. although michelangelo would last tell us — liked present parthenogenetic wonder — art training. born 1475 line minor florentine nobility, entered workshop domenico ghirlandaio pupil-apprentice age 13. fastidious painter may learned practice, uncommon time, making preparatory drawings work permanent mediums.yet michelangelo’s self-starter claims may still stand scrutiny. according dates assigned drawings near beginning show, could sketching figures frescoes giotto masaccio local churches early 16. small oil-and-tempera painting called “the torment saint anthony,” based print martin schongauer, came time ghirlandaio stint. it’s impressive: teenage artist skillfully edits schongauer’s midair tangle demons-and-saint, sets invented seascape.by 1490-91, seems come tutelage bertoldo di giovanni. significant older sculptor, bertoldo also curator antiquities collection lorenzo de’ medici amassed enhance social status family. michelangelo, interlude formative. confirmed sculpture medium cared deeply; exposed classical tradition would emulate transform; initiated lifelong medici connection would boon curse.but questions came first arise too, centered marble sculpture called “young archer.” many years, figure nude youth stood, barely noticed, cultural services french embassy fifth avenue, across street met. 1996, art historian identified michelangelo. call hotly debated, attribution stood. “circa 1496-97” date attached work makes altogether possible michelangelo carved figure age 21, making prodigy claimed be.with sculpture, found would favorite subject, one would make name: heroic male body. approximately decade “young archer” came colossal “david,” michelangelo star, medici darling, way becoming new kind public celebrity aimed be: highly skilled maker things, multitasking, miracle-working aristocrat creativity called genius. michelangelo didn’t coin term, (with reluctant nod leonardo da vinci) coined type.prestigious commissions, painting, sculpture architecture, piled up. 1504, asked fresco council chamber palazzo della signoria, seat florentine government. leonardo, 30 years senior, friend, assigned opposite wall. idea would paint historic battle, michelangelo’s one troop 14th-century florentine soldiers interrupted swim arno take enemy surprise.he turned scene polyphonic chorale pumped bodies: abs, pecs, lats, glutes, buns. know image well, though fresco — thanks first would endless medici interventions — never got beyond full-scale cartoon stage. ink chalk sketches paper individual figures exist. drawing whole composition, smudged looks like puff smoke. vivid piece evidence large 1540 oil painting bastiano da sangallo, saw finished cartoon whitewashed out.all material, scattered among museums — louvre, uffizi, albertina vienna — brought together met. exhibition, organized carmen c. bambach, curator museum’s department drawings prints, works. ingeniously reconstructs michelangelo projects assembling related designs dense, connect-the-dots clusters.this is, course, way present architecturally scaled art, long-vanished things. show close get seeing massive sculptural tomb pope julius ii many aborted iterations; “urgent” commission (years julius’s death) pulled michelangelo battle fresco. selection plans — scribbled paper scraps, spread across pasted-together sheets — facade medici parish church san lorenzo adds beguiling archive thinking-in-progress. rarely architectural design felt expressively personal, moody, painterly, calligraphic.part ms. bambach’s goal, one pursues labor-of-love catalog, revisit original renaissance concept design — disegno — theoretical category, aesthetic ethical end itself. basic idea physical world represented, every shade contour, divine labor so, human level, (or could) art. michelangelo benefited mightily elevation artist workshop drone deity (and brand). later megastar years, people actually referred god. sistine chapel ceiling work disegno excelsis: story creation told superhuman craft.the exhibition’s long central gallery given ceiling, project complex michelangelo gave organizing production team job himself. see plugging away it, scaffolding ceiling, self-caricature drawn margin handwritten sonnet. “i’ve already grown goiter drudgery,” grouses. “my brush, time, drips paint, turning face perfect drop cloth.”in sistine paintings — male body — nearly bodies male — muscle top muscle, arnold schwarzenegger circa 1975. classical ideal — balance, just-rightness — pumped existence. mannerist too-muchness — 21st century knows lot — rules. neither ceiling, later, nightmarish “last judgment,” art you’re invited love. aims overpower you, make feel small, crushed cosmic history. viewers find experience thrill. i’ve always found off-putting.it’s drawings start feel close art maker. one chalk-sketched titan oddly lumpy, imperfect, maybe-not-young body; he’s sleeping. clearly, he’s studio assistant who’s roped posing end day. mood “last judgment” fresco full-orchestra cataclysmic, ink sketches light, almost tender. one, resurrected dead float space, speck-like weightless, like birds lifting foggy lake.and drawings generated tenderness itself. true gallery devoted fanciful “divine heads,” including one doleful cleopatra, middle-aged artist made gifts young male aristocrats — gherardo perini, andrea quaratesi, tommaso de’ cavalieri — developed crushes. black chalk portrait quaratesi, 37 years junior, somber dreamboat plush lips faraway eyes it’s eye-stopper. several discreetly erotic mythological drawings gave valentines cavalieri who, whatever sexual nature bond, became lifelong friend. artist’s bedside died 88 rome 1564.and city, michelangelo spent last 30 years life, met poet intellectual vittoria colonna. friendship came late (he 61), lasted colonna’s death 1547, seems seriously changed him. encouraged move contemplative direction brought new soft grace work. michelangelo be, often is, visually aggressive artist. isn’t — quite opposite — meltingly sinuous red-and-black chalk “dead christ held mother” late 1530s, great black chalk “pietà” around 1546 dedicated colonna, gave her.but essential ways didn’t change. late career, still workaholic, overbooking commissions, pacifying popes, writing poetry, cooking designs artists (sebastiano del piombo, daniele da volterra) turn paintings. hand mind never still. never been. nearly every drawing met show work sheet. artist makes sketch, rotates make second, turns adds yet another. images given sheet might include bodybuilders, saints, architectural elevations, pornographic doodle, man screaming, verse petrarch, beloved face. genius, monuments made these.
